precis:
Amendments to the SHIP'S TONNAGE SURVEY AND MEASUREMENT FEES REGULATIONS
which increase most existing fees and introduce new fees for the
verification of tonnage calculations performed by a surveyor of ships
("fee for office" appointees) and for surveys and measurements done outside
of normal working hours, effective July 1, 1995.
